<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.4">
<l>vāraṇinta mulaimaṭavāy vaitēvī viṇṇappam</l>
<l>tēraṇinta vayōttiyarkōṉ peruntēvī kēṭṭaruḷāy</l>
<l>kūraṇinta vēlvalavaṉ kukaṉōṭum kaṅkaitaṉṉil</l>
<l>cīraṇinta tōḻamai koṇ ṭatumōra ṭaiyāḷam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lady with breasts wrapped in a bodice!</l>
<l rend="indent">Vaidehī! Salutations.</l>
<l>Great goddess of the king of Ayodhyā</l>
<l rend="indent">adorned with chariots, graciously listen,</l>
<l>on the Ganges, [he] accepted a friendship,</l>
<l rend="indent">imbued with excellence, with Guha,</l>
<l rend="indent">skilled with a sharp spear.</l>
<l>This is one proof.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
